title: Voodoo Bear
extract: Definition of voodoo (Entry 2 of 3) 1 : of, relating to, or practicing voodoo voodoo rituals. 2 : based on highly improbable suppositions : extremely implausible or unrealistic voodoo economics. voodoo. verb.
